<HL>
   Beard Oil Co. Stock Buy-Back
</HL>
<DATE>
04/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B8
</SO>
<CO>
   BOC
</CO>
<IN>
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   OKLAHOMA CITY -- Beard Oil Co. said its board authorized
the repurchase of as many as 300,000 of the company's common
stock outstanding.
   The company said the shares will be purchased periodically
in the open market or private transactions, and will be held
for general corporate purchases.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   The authorization covers nearly 5% of the company's
5,869,651 common shares outstanding at year end.
</TEXT>
